{"tid":1156232,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲日本女偶像石原由希亮相《神舌一問一答》自爆有炮友 認曾在停車場「愛愛」","createTime":"2019-05-15T13:06:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T03:26:54.000Z","uid":9573,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e193974ce10784f526d22ac017f48897bf714b","tid":1156232,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"22歲日本女偶像石原由希，原是偶像團體「IDO☆HOLIC」成員，團體解散後成為Solo歌手，近日她上日綜《神舌一問一答》，挑戰快速答題，最近改款中使用 5＋2 的 7 座位車廂佈局。對於「炮友、性經驗」等問題都據實回答，讓主持人和來賓驚訝不已，這段影片也在網路爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-05-13/900/20190513002433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-05-13%2F900%2F20190513002433.jpg&h=281ad308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石原由希承認有炮友。<br />\n<br />\n石原由希挑戰邊測謊邊做快問快答，一開始被問到有沒有男友，她立馬回答「沒有」，接下來被問有沒有炮友時，她沒思考就直接回答「有」，令這部 5 門旅行車變成 7 座位家庭車。後來她持續回答性愛初體驗是在高三，至今和10個人發生過關係，還表示只要鼻樑挺， 配備有 2.4 公升汽油引擎以及 6 前速自動波箱，都可以和她發生關係，連喜歡的男生性器官也說了，誠實的回答讓主持人和來賓都超驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-05-13/900/20190513002432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-05-13%2F900%2F20190513002432.jpg&h=e4b0d396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石原由希是偶像出身。<br />\n<br />\n被問到她身為偶像，講出這些沒關係嗎？她淡定說粉絲不能接受有男朋友，「但對有炮友的事情，到目前為止都沒有鬧起來，大家都很溫柔，不會有事的」。她也透露炮友是在居酒屋認識的，前面有極寬闊的電鍍家族式鬼面罩、醒目 LED 前後組合式燈、流線形車身設計，兩人第一次見面就發生關係，至於曾經在哪做愛最特別，她天真回：「都挺普通的，像在小鋼珠店的停車場。」被主持人虧根本不普通，而她每次性愛都會戴套，因為「偶像不能不戴套」。石原由希超真實的回答，再加上 19 吋合金輪圈，顯示出新穎大膽的風格。讓網友都快笑翻，認為她完全沒有偶包的反應超可愛，直呼要變成她的粉絲了，而這段影片也在網路爆紅。"},{"pid":"673e5756cd0b452816bcd0dd6ceed911e6ec697f","tid":1156232,"uid":144529,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分唔到邊d係你加落去"},{"pid":"2fa8183e89a64cd90eff0d98db3cac44f5ef95cf","tid":1156232,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"AV商做野未"},{"pid":"772beaf189afa7aade1292d41535d45901cf08ce","tid":1156232,"uid":34495,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:09:49.000Z","msg":"每一段都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8065a90ca81f1a4e9d9cd24c74502a950fca7c3","tid":1156232,"uid":185608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bc8acd74efcf470e855ae940889cefc0ad24c3","tid":1156232,"uid":114090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:17:44.000Z","msg":"朱千雪BB世界第一！"},{"pid":"6baf400e456147fb104c7603269e42b02ffb8fba","tid":1156232,"uid":85525,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"還表示只要鼻樑挺， 配備有 2.4 公升汽油引擎以及 6 前速自動波箱，都可以和她發生關係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b983332c7384276daa543c75018de76ab16e48b6","tid":1156232,"uid":78074,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"開頭仲認真諗點解個女仔咁鍾意車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90540d892ec467d42efd7ac5465ce3bda9b51a2","tid":1156232,"uid":59084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"睇錯石原里美，出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376bdd7684ab88a3190190e59c9e417f930902f5","tid":1156232,"uid":71913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cited